{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
Remember w[G]hen,  [Em7]  Life [Cadd9]began a second ti[D]me,
I found your ha[G]nd [Em7], and you fin[Cadd9]ally found mi[D]ne,
I lived be[G]fore, but then I kn[Em7]ew,
My wo[Cadd9]rld started with [D]you,
Remember w[G]hen[Em7][C][Dsus][D]
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
Remember w[G]hen,[Em7]   We vowed the [Cadd9]vows and walked the w[D]alk,
Gave our hea[G]rts,[Em7]    and saw it al[Cadd9]l pay o[D]ff,
