There was[Cadd9] joy and hard w[D]ork,
Remember w[G]hen[Em7][C][Dsus][D]
{end_of_verse}


{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
Remember w[G]hen,[Em7]   old ones[Cadd9] die and new were b[D]orn,
Life was cha[G]nged,[Em7]   disa[Cadd9]ssembled, rearran[D]ged,
We moved out we[G]st, to chase the [Em7]sun,
We [Cadd9]found our way and kept it f[D]un,
Remember w[G]hen
{end_of_verse}

